{"tid":1824370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《空姐牛肉飯事件》大家唔好再咁順攤跟狗番狗屋","createTime":"2020-01-14T11:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T18:35:09.000Z","uid":172454,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"62e91ea073c591e6cae512e7a9856ff4e5583135","tid":1824370,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:25:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/police_powers/q9.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FpoliceAndCrime%2Fpolice_powers%2Fq9.shtml&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSeroPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=9bde28c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/police_powers/q9.shtml</a><br />\n跟據當場情況，個學生應該只係被要求協助調查，市民<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">並無責任</span></strong>去提供協助或前往警署。<br />\n如果大家忙冇時間既係絕對可以拒絕，就算翻左去警署都可以隨時離開，除非當場被捕。<br />\n而當場被捕時警員<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>必須告知</strong></span>你被捕原因和涉嫌所犯罪行，而且過程中你係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有權保持緘默</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n為左保護自己或者其它人既權利，大家要清楚知道依點，唔好再戇尻尻咁佢話點就點。"},{"pid":"3e38e3f64dc689fdab256d691883ff4ab14809f7","tid":1824370,"uid":107681,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"寫係咁寫，現實佢成班捉你可以點<br />\n<br />\n你隻手推下d豆腐狗都告你襲狗"},{"pid":"e15e725da19e5c2e12a79ee4c36a3cb917ced6b3","tid":1824370,"uid":3443,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3e38e3f64dc689fdab256d691883ff4ab14809f7","tid":1824370,"uid":107681,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"寫係咁寫，現實佢成班捉你可以點<br />\n<br />\n你隻手推下d豆腐狗都告你襲狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"樓主不如試下行出冷氣房睇下個現實世界先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講就咁講"},{"pid":"5a1ac54c757cbdf68f46580e03dd283e62786799","tid":1824370,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"「如果大家忙冇時間既係絕對可以拒絕」<br />\n唔洗講到咁曲<br />\n